subtitle: My personal website and portfolio, you are experiencing V2 right now!
paragraphs: This is my personal website and portfolio, you are experiencing V2 right now! It's quite the upgrade from the previous version, which was the first thing I tried building with React. This one is also built with React.js and I chose to go with Sass, if you haven't heard from Kevin Powell try checking out his youtube channel, I'm sure you are going to end up loving Sass as well.
